snippet.title: NumWorlds on iOS and Android Teaser
snippet.description:
Welcome to NumWorlds, the perfect game for those moments when you need a mindful break or just want to flex those cognitive muscles!

Addictive Math Puzzle Game 🧩
Sharpen your brain with daily challenges 🧠
Explore fantastic levels and worlds 🌐

⬇️DOWNLOAD THE GAME NOW ⬇️
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/app/numworlds/id6736342660
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.blackpugstudio.numworlds
